==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stumbling-block
<hw>Stum"bling-block`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any cause of
stumbling, perplexity, or error.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We preach Christ crucified, unto the Jews a
<qex>stumbling-block</qex>, and unto the Greeks foolishness.</q>
<rj><qau>1 Cor. i. 23.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stumblingly</ent>⟦br⟧
